SUMMARY:News Startup Sessions with INN and Tiny News Collective
DESCRIPTION:Join the Institute for Nonprofit News (INN) and Tiny News Collective for News Startup Sessions. The small group sessions will take place with INN’s Courtney Lewis\, TNC’s membership director Elaine Díaz Rodríguez\, and a few other leaders looking to launch a news operation. \nIn these sessions\, you’ll: \n\nGain insight into key elements for success\nGet answers to your pressing questions\nDiscover resources to support your journey\n\nGet a head start with INN’s Startup Guide — packed with early tips and resources for planning\, launching\, and running a nonprofit news organization. See you soon.
URL:https://inn.org/event/news-startup-sessions-inn-tiny-news-collective-2/2026-03-17/
CATEGORIES:Services
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://inn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/300-x-250-_-CTA-with-TNC-6.png
END:VEVENT
