SUMMARY:2026 Nonprofit News Awards
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the best in nonprofit news at the 2026 Nonprofit News Awards! \nThe evening will begin Tuesday\, June 16\, at 5 p.m. with a reception featuring light hors d’oeuvres and drinks\, followed by the awards ceremony from 6 to 8:30 p.m.\, when the winners will be announced.
URL:https://inn.org/event/2026-nonprofit-news-awards/
